# Site

The content of the website of Francesco Saccone, available at
<https://francescosaccone.com/>.

## Structure

Each .md file is a page and is translated to HTML using
[lowdown](https://kristaps.bsd.lv/lowdown/).

Every .md file is accompanied by the following files:

- The corresponding .md.desc file contains the description of the page.

- The corresponding .md.time file contains the creation timestamp of the page
  on the first line and the last modification timestamp on the second one.

- The corresponding .md.title file contains the title of the page.
